OL,6,FPatrick Roach, general secretary of
OL,7,Fthe NASUWT, said: "The fact that
OL,8,Fteachers are at the top of the list of
OL,9,Fprofessions working unpaid overtime is
OL,10,Fyet further shameful evidence of the
OL,11,FGovernment's failure to invest
OL,12,Fproperly in our schools and colleges.
OL,14,F"Teachers are seeing their workloads
OL,15,Fpiled higher and higher and, with cuts
OL,16,Fto support staff and cuts to other
OL,17,Fchildren's services, teachers are now
OL,18,Fworking around the clock.
