OL,6,F"Unmanageable workload is the main
OL,7,Fdriver of teachers leaving, alongside
OL,8,Fexcessive accountability.
OL,10,F"Graduates look to teaching and the
OL,11,Fcurrent education climate and
OL,12,Funsurprisingly opt for other
OL,13,Fprofessions rather than be underpaid
OL,14,Ffor excessive hours spent in buildings
OL,15,Fthat are falling apart thanks to a
OL,16,Fmiserly Government."
OL,18,FThe TUC dubbed Friday "Work Your
OL,19,FProper Hours Day", urging workers to
OL,20,Ftake the breaks they are entitled to
OL,21,Fand finish their shifts on time.
