OL,6,FManagers were encouraged to support
OL,7,Fstaff by setting reasonable workloads
OL,8,Fand putting in place workplace
OL,9,Fpolicies to protect against burnout.
OL,11,FThe TUC said 3.8 million people did
OL,12,Funpaid overtime in 2023, worth
OL,13,Fthousands of pounds a year for every
OL,14,Fworker.
OL,16,FTwo out of five teachers did unpaid
OL,17,Fovertime, according to the report.
OL,19,FOther professions with high rates of
OL,20,Funpaid overtime included health and
OL,21,Fsocial services managers.
